                            Divo Marco An <lb n="2"/>tonino Pio <expan><abbr>patr</abbr><ex>i</ex></expan> <lb n="3"/>[[<expan><abbr>Imp</abbr><ex>eratoris</ex></expan> <expan><abbr>Caes</abbr><ex>aris</ex></expan> <expan><abbr>M</abbr><ex>arci</ex></expan> <expan><abbr>Aureli</abbr><ex>i</ex></expan> <lb n="4"/>Commodi Antoni <lb n="5"/>ni]] <expan><abbr>Aug</abbr><ex>usti</ex></expan> [[<expan><abbr>Germ</abbr><ex>anici</ex></expan> <expan><abbr>Sarm</abbr><ex>anici</ex></expan> <expan><abbr>pont</abbr><ex>ificis</ex></expan> <lb n="6"/><expan><abbr>max</abbr><ex>imi</ex></expan> <expan><abbr>trib</abbr><ex>unicia</ex></expan> <expan><abbr>pot</abbr><ex>estate</ex></expan> VI co<expan><ex>n</ex><abbr>s</abbr><ex>ulis</ex></expan> III]] <lb n="7"/><expan><abbr>p</abbr><ex>atris</ex></expan> <expan><abbr>p</abbr><ex>atriae</ex></expan> <lb n="8"/><expan><abbr>r</abbr><ex>es</ex></expan> <expan><abbr>p</abbr><ex>ublica</ex></expan> <expan><abbr>m</abbr><ex>unicipii</ex></expan> <expan><abbr>H</abbr><ex>adriani</ex></expan> <expan><abbr>D</abbr><ex>robetensium</ex></expan>.
                        
                        
                    </ab>

                
                
            </div>

            
           <div type="translation" xml:lang="fr">
                <p>                    Au bienheureux Marcus Antoninus Pius, père de (l'empereur César Marc Aurèle Commode Antonin) Auguste, (vainqueur des Germains, vainqueur des Sarmates, grand pontife, investi avec la puissance tribunicienne pour la sixième fois, consul trois fois), père de la patrie, la communauté du municipe Hadrianum Drobeta.</p>
                    <desc><ref type="license" target="http://creativecommons.org/licenses/by-sa/3.0/">Licensed under a Creative Commons Attribution-ShareAlike 3.0 Unported licence.</ref>
                </desc>
            </div>
            

            <div type="commentary">
                <p>Les l. 3-5, martelées, contiennent le nom de l'empereur Commode.</p>
            </div>

